headlines.description: — Damian Lillard acknowledged this season opener felt a little different from the others as he adjusted to switching teams for the first time.
headlines.shortLinkText: Lillard scores 39 points in his Bucks debut to help Milwaukee edge the Philadelphia 76ers 118-117

events.name: Phoenix Suns at Los Angeles Lakers

headlines.description: — When Kevin Durant scored in the final minutes, LeBron James answered. These two generational basketball greats put on a scintillating duel in their first head-to-head matchup in nearly five years.
headlines.shortLinkText: LeBron James keys Lakers' 4th-quarter rally for 100-95 win over Kevin Durant's short-handed Suns
